<br>
One final note, if you can get in a group that doesn't care about chump change that drops off mobs in chardok and Sebilis, volunteer to &quot;clean up the corpses&quot;. This seemed to work alot better before luclin camp out, when peopel were really trying to accumulate cash like everyone seems to be now.... it used to be I could get in a seb group and no one really cared about the cash that would drop, so I could just scoop it up, and make a few 100pp while getting xp. turn the rare loot and gems over to other and generally no one complains.<br>
<br>
-Chiriko <p><center>
